result.name: Legends of India

reviews.text:
Fairly average curry house. Food was not too bad, but the curries seemed a bit formulaic, i.e. meat/fish plus a sauce.
Overall rather similar to some of the other Kowloon curry houses like Gaylord, however that place has a bit more charm.
Also worth bearing in mind that they do a 15% discount for HSBC credit cards.
If you are in Hong Kong and want tasty Indian food and beer... go for it.. you will not regret... super hospitality and great taste.. ymmmm
Worst place for indian food , its a dance bar , never go here at any cost ! If u r a vegetarian , u cant even sit there with family !

Gud food 
Must visit if want to taste Indian authentic food

result.name: Legends of India

reviews.text:
喀什米爾咖哩馬鈴薯🍛
咖哩帶甜味及椰奶味，口感香滑，不嗜辣又鐘意咖哩嘅一定要試下！薯仔份量少但表面炸過，香脆得嚟又熱辣辣！
.
鑊仔羊肉🐑💦
一貫印度菜嘅重口味風格，少少辣又唔會嗆口，味道層次豐富。但羊肉煮得太耐，口感太硬，肉味流失晒。
.
Naan🍽
即製嘅Naan好出色，食完一客又一客。Garlic Naan同堆butter Naan只係lightly seasoned，唔會喧賓奪主。咖哩雖然好食，都需要有Naan配搭。
.
番茄湯🍅
本身睇相以為係類似Moroccan tomato soup。但飲落番茄味啖，香料味濃，亦更加creamy🤤。 .
Legends of India位於尖沙咀寶勒巷某商業大廈，本來只因半價而光顧，但一嚐後發現食物質素奇高。惠顧當日正如男友所言，我地一枱都包到場。
